784
00:40:46,993 --> 00:40:48,369
Kerja bagus.

785
00:40:48,619 --> 00:40:54,917
Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima,
enam, tujuh, delapan.

786
00:40:55,251 --> 00:41:01,132
Delapan, tujuh, enam, lima, empat,
